2017-04-14  [Michael Rasmussen] 3.15.0-26-g73d489107

	* src/plugins/vcalendar/vcal_manager.c
	* src/plugins/vcalendar/vcal_meeting_gtk.c
	* src/plugins/vcalendar/vcalendar.c		
