		Fix a Win32-specific syntax error.

2015-07-01  [Andrej Kacian] 3.11.1-188-g226efcbfa

	* src/folder.c		
		Fix a logic error introduced in previous commit.

2015-07-01  [Andrej Kacian] 3.11.1-187-g567b040b6

	* src/alertpanel.h
	* src/folder.c
	* src/folder.h
	* src/foldersel.c
	* src/mh_gtk.c
